column5: I saw some sleds out on the big lake last night, any word on the ice conditions. There was a few out fishing today, any luck? Im gonna head out tomorrow drill some holes, and try for some whities.
4 of us were out today.  Anywhere from 5" to 1" of ice  Got out to 85 FOW.....and one area you are in 5" and 10 feet away is 1". Won't be doing that again.
Hope you at least let Andy lead !
85 FOW, wow Did you get any fish at least? I am hoping to get into 60-70 fow tomorrow
There's no fish in Lake Simcoe !!!!!  No, we marked a few but didn't get any  Wayne.....Andy's not a leader....  .......  He's a talker.....
